summary: An ordinance amending Sections 4, 7, 16, 17, 18, 19, 23, 26, 27, 28, 29, 30, 31, 32, 34, 35, 41, 42, 54, 56, 58, 60, 61, 63, 68, 90, 91 of Ordinance No. 24392, entitled: "An ordinance regulating the installation and operation of electrical wires, appliances and apparatus in or about the buildings in the City of Seattle and providing penalties for violation thereof" approved June 15, 1910.
